name: George Baker Selection
description: '''George Baker Selection''' was a pop-rock band from [[Assendelft]], the [[Netherlands]]. The band is best-known for the 1969 song "[[Little Green Bag]]", the 1975 world-wide hit "[[Paloma Blanca]]" (one of the most played songs in history){{cn|date=November 2025}}, and the 1985 Pan European hit "[[Santa Lucia by Night]]".
